s for you!"],[3916,4024,"Get down!"],[4024,4095,"No!"],[4095,4200,"What are you doing?"],[4200,4258,"Do you want to make"],[4258,4433,"your commission or not?"],[4533,4658,"Don't touch me!"],[4658,4742,"No! Don’t touch me."],[4742,4929,"The stupid slut surrogate like you"],[4929,5059,"doesn't deserve to be wearing"],[5059,5155,"a dress worth hundreds"],[5155,5284,"of thousands of dollars."],[5734,5839,"Get it off!"],[5964,6126,"Get away from my fiancée."],[6126,6185,"Oscar!"]],"31":[[0,137,"Oscar!"],[1100,1200,"Oscar."],[2477,2560,"What were you doing"],[2560,2669,"with my fiancée?"],[2669,2773,"Nothing. Nothing."],[2773,2890,"I was helping this woman"],[2890,3073,"deal with the, the, the surrogate."],[3073,3174,"Open your eyes"],[3174,3253,"and see for yourself."],[3253,3436,"This is my fiancée."],[3507,3574,"She lied."],[3574,3745,"She claimed to be your fiancée."],[3745,3874,"She even had the"],[3874,3983,"the black card."],[4004,4133,"Black card?"],[4262,4421,"Well, if she's so rich."],[4421,4521,"Let's make her pay"],[4521,4683,"for my fiancée's ruined dress."],[4683,4829,"Plus medical expenses,"],[4829,4996,"and emotional damage."],[5021,5184,"Total in one million dollars."],[5296,5455,"Oscar, I didn't mean to."],[5935,6085,"This is the unlimited black card"],[6085,6222,"that you were talking about?"]],"32":[[4,120,"This is the unlimited black"],[120,316,"card that you were talking about?"],[579,700,"This is a fake card."],[825,921,"She lied."],[942,1030,"Oscar,"],[1059,1288,"I only did it because I love you."],[1343,1472,"Please."],[1518,1697,"Steven, have the Sinclair"],[1697,1918,"Group legal team write her a letter."],[1918,2173,"She must pay the million dollars."],[2264,2348,"Yes, sir."],[2560,2660,"And as for him,"],[2761,2844,"fire him."],[2907,2982,"The Sinclair Group"],[2982,3153,"will never hire this man again."],[3153,3274,"You damn thief!"],[3274,3457,"You cost me my job."],[3457,3553,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[3553,3753,"please just give me another chance."],[3820,3920,"Oscar, I can't believe"],[3920,3999,"you did this to me"],[3999,4200,"for some surrogate slut."],[4200,4400,"She's just a bitch."],[4496,4575,"Let’s go."],[5121,5359,"Chloe, didn’t you want a daddy?"],[5401,5455,"Mommy’s going to"],[5455,5584,"find one for you now."]],"33":[[750,888,"Were you scared?"],[967,1105,"I know I promised you that I wouldn't"],[1105,1297,"let anyone bully you again."],[1297,1393,"I was late."],[1551,1705,"I'm sorry."],[2302,2552,"She said that she was your fiancée."],[2552,2648,"Who?"],[2648,2744,"Mia?"],[3307,3411,"Look, I'm sorry, okay?"],[3411,3486,"I should have told you"],[3486,3707,"about my past relationships."],[3732,3895,"Mia is my ex."],[3895,3970,"But we broke up"],[3970,4099,"because my relationship with"],[4099,4254,"her fell apart."],[4254,4333,"But she said that"],[4333,4521,"she was your fiancée."]],"34":[[450,729,"You are my only fiancée."],[729,967,"And to avoid any misunderstanding,"],[967,1088,"I'll hold this banquet"],[1088,1255,"immediately."],[2181,2385,"Oscar, is there gonna be a lot of people?"],[2385,2527,"There are, but they're here"],[2527,2681,"to celebrate us."],[3215,3457,"Don't worry, I'm here."],[3457,3566,"I'll go greet them first,"],[3566,3732,"and you come down when you're ready."],[4233,4346,"It seems like Mr. Sinclair"],[4346,4483,"really loves you."],[4483,4567,"This gown was custom"],[4567,4692,"made just for you."],[4692,4821,"It arrived yesterday,"],[4821,4950,"flown in from Italy."],[4950,5146,"It's worth over $200,000."]],"35":[[717,821,"Ladies and gentlemen."],[1009,1184,"I'm so glad you're all here to witness"],[1184,1443,"the most important moment of my life."],[1543,1651,"I want to tell you all that"],[1651,1743,"I have found the most"],[1743,1985,"important person in my life."],[2060,2181,"My wife."],[2535,2740,"And now, let's welcome"],[2740,2840,"Phoebe."],[3453,3661,"Oh, she's stunning."],[3661,3828,"Exactly."],[3828,3920,"I would marry her too,"],[3920,4037,"if I were Oscar."]],"36":[[1626,1776,"This is the woman I plan on spending"],[1776,1947,"the rest of my life with."],[2093,2306,"I didn't give her a proper proposal."],[2414,2560,"I want to make it up to her now."],[2560,2635,"In the presence"],[2635,2840,"of friends and family."],[3311,3411,"Phoebe,"],[3482,3628,"will you marry me?"],[3899,3991,"Daddy!"],[4333,4454,"I object!"]],"37":[[1038,1184,"Mia, what are you doing here?"],[1184,1334,"Daddy, I'm Chloe."],[1380,1438,"Oh my God,"],[1438,1614,"did that kid just call Oscar daddy?"],[1693,1947,"Has to be Oscar's ex-girlfriend, Mia."],[1947,2097,"This is insane."],[2097,2306,"His ex showing up with a child"],[2306,2439,"to his engagement party?"],[2473,2594,"This is going to be good."],[3132,3274,"Daddy, I missed you."],[3424,3566,"What the hell is this?"],[3636,3732,"Grandpa,"],[3732,3791,"looks like you have"],[3791,3958,"another great granddaughter."],[4004,4095,"I'm sure Oscar will"],[4095,4208,"take care of this."],[4220,4316,"Oscar."],[4316,4504,"Chloe and I missed you so much."],[4504,4804,"Daddy, I’m Chloe, we finally met."],[4900,5030,"Did she just call you daddy?"]],"38":[[37,141,"That's not my child."],[141,283,"I don't know who that is."],[283,367,"I'm going to figure it out,"],[367,550,"and give you an explanation."],[550,675,"Mia, I don't recall us"],[675,846,"having a child together."],[917,1001,"Knock this off,"],[1001,1084,"or I'm going to get security"],[1084,1184,"to kick you out."],[1184,1267,"Oscar,"],[1267,1359,"you told me that you didn't"],[1359,1476,"want to have a baby with me,"],[1476,1593,"then we broke up."],[1634,1864,"But turns out, I was already pregnant."],[1947,2056,"What?"],[2056,2185,"So Oscar's the jerk"],[2185,2285,"who broke up with Mia while"],[2285,2377,"she was pregnant?"],[2485,2610,"Okay, I need you to clarify this"],[2610,2677,"in front of everyone."],[2677,2806,"You cheated on me, okay?"],[2806,2948,"It wasn't the other way around."],[2948,3123,"It was a misunderstanding."],[3370,3670,"I would never, ever hurt you."],[3712,3924,"I loved you so much."],[3924,4070,"I'm asking you to leave."],[4070,4254,"Leave now, or I'm calling security."],[4254,4408,"Daddy, don't yell at mommy."],[4850,5121,"Well, I have the DNA test report"],[5121,5234,"right here,"],[5234,5388,"which proves that Chloe"],[5388,5559,"is in fact, your daughter."],[5559,5626,"Take a look."]],"39":[[909,996,"Well,"],[996,1297,"due to unforeseen circumstances,"],[1322,1480,"this banquet is over."],[1480,1559,"Grandpa!"],[2786,2848,"Hey."],[3361,3424,"Wait, wait, wait, wait!"],[3424,3482,"Grandpa,"],[3516,3632,"what are you doing?"],[3841,3978,"Mia can't stay here."],[3978,4095,"Oscar,"],[4095,4166,"I've never known"],[4166,4362,"you to be irresponsible."],[4362,4512,"Chloe is your daughter."],[4512,4671,"And I will not have a Sinclair"],[4671,4829,"left out in the cold."],[4829,5034,"But I already have a happy family."],[5155,5292,"I only want Phoebe."]],"40":[[8,145,"This banquet was for her."],[145,325,"It wasn't for some child"],[325,467,"or any inheritance."],[579,650,"Do you think you could just"],[650,759,"abandon Chloe?"],[759,884,"I mean completely?"],[884,1026,"Am I supposed to be responsible"],[1026,1138,"for some random child"],[1138,1263,"because of a paternity test"],[1263,1426,"that someone could forge?"],[1426,1514,"If that's the case,"],[1514,1672,"I'll forge 100 grandsons for you"],[1672,1776,"now, Grandpa."],[1810,1889,"Oscar,"],[1993,2147,"you could yell at me,"],[2147,2448,"but our sweet baby, Chloe,"],[2452,2573,"she's innocent."],[2627,2857,"Daddy, do you hate me?"],[2923,3090,"Do you not want me anymore?"],[3211,3299,"Okay."],[3299,3516,"You can get another paternity test."],[3516,3691,"But until those results come back,"],[3691,3791,"they're staying here."],[3791,3920,"End of story."]],"41":[[1272,1380,"Hi, Mia."],[1380,1459,"I'm William,"],[1459,1564,"for the next few days,"],[1564,1651,"I’d love to take care of"],[1651,1730,"you and your daughter."],[1801,1897,"Thank you."],[3215,3278,"Phoebe,"],[3415,3616,"you have to believe me."],[3845,4008,"Oscar, I'm tired."],[4008,4204,"Kind of just"],[4204,4287,"want to have some space"],[4287,4471,"for myself tonight."],[4913,5092,"God damn it!"],[5347,5405,"Mommy."],[5463,5722,"Isn't Daddy already in heaven?"],[5722,5880,"Why do I have to call Uncle Oscar"],[5880,5980,"my dad now?"],[5980,6072,"Shh."],[6072,6327,"Oscar is your new daddy now."],[6327,6377,"But-"],[6377,6485,"No buts."],[6635,6694,"You don't want to"],[6694,6873,"end up homeless, do you?"],[7011,7098,"Right."],[7098,7319,"So you call Oscar Daddy now."],[7524,7707,"We need to get rid of Phoebe, too."]],"42":[[538,658,"Seems Oscar having a"],[658,834,"daughter hit you pretty hard."],[834,913,"Wait."],[913,1021,"What's the rush?"],[1021,1134,"Let's have a chat."],[1447,1518,"We don't have anything"],[1518,1605,"to talk about."],[1605,1664,"Sure we do."],[1722,1851,"Aren't you the least bit curious"],[1851,2031,"as to why Oscar and I broke up?"],[2223,2439,"Oscar and I were the perfect match."],[2439,2552,"Everybody knows that."],[3199,3319,"Daddy, Mommy went to find"],[3319,3399,"Aunt Phoebe."],[3399,3457,"What?"],[3486,3570,"Where is she?"],[3570,3636,"By the pool."],[3636,3741,"I'll take you there."]],"43":[[0,45,"If you're just going to"],[45,120,"brag about your past,"],[120,254,"I don't think it's necessary."],[254,396,"Don't leave so quick."],[1259,1309,"I know that"],[1309,1426,"the only reason you're with Oscar"],[1426,1551,"is because he's paying you."],[1597,1639,"Look,"],[1705,1747,"I'll double"],[1747,1864,"whatever he's giving you"],[1935,1981,"as long as you"],[1981,2093,"promise to leave Oscar"],[2093,2235,"and give him back to Chloe."],[3048,3174,"Fine, I agree."],[3211,3374,"I knew it."],[3374,3516,"No one can say no to money."]],"44":[[29,116,"Phoebe, you're really going"],[116,262,"to leave me for money?"],[262,346,"Daddy,"],[346,525,"what are they talking about?"],[638,754,"Nothing."],[754,817,"Let's go."],[1789,1906,"Are you kidding me?"],[2006,2093,"What makes you think"],[2093,2210,"you're worth nine hundred and"],[2210,2370,"ninety-nine million dollars?"],[2469,2540,"Didn't you say I could"],[2540,2681,"put any number I wanted?"],[3203,3299,"If you're broke,"],[3299,3440,"just say that."],[4533,4617,"Aunt Phoebe!"],[4662,4754,"Sit here."],[4900,5034,"That's okay, don’t worry about me,"],[5034,5192,"I can just sit here."],[5192,5267,"No, sit here."],[5267,5342,"Take my spot."],[5342,5459,"I don't mind."],[5839,6026,"What's the matter with Oscar?"],[6026,6126,"Why is he being so cold"],[6126,6231,"all of a sudden?"],[6877,6973,"Aunt Phoebe,"],[6973,7136,"why did you push me?"],[7215,7273,"I didn't."]],"45":[[4,125,"I didn't."],[125,300,"Daddy, it hurts."],[379,579,"Chloe. Chloe?"],[579,696,"What's going on?"],[696,838,"How did this happen?"],[838,959,"Aunt Phoebe was mad"],[959,1184,"because I was sitting next to Daddy."],[1309,1514,"And then I gave her the seat."],[1514,1643,"But she was still mad,"],[1643,1785,"and then she pushed me."],[1822,1951,"That's not true, I didn’t..."],[1951,2152,"Oh. You didn't?"],[2152,2235,"Okay."],[2235,2431,"Are you saying that she's lying?"],[2431,2494,"Do you even think"],[2494,2590,"she knows how to lie?"],[2590,2802,"She's literally a five-year-old girl."],[2802,2957,"If anything happens to her,"],[2957,3019,"you will pay-"],[3019,3115,"Mia, let's just get"],[3115,3282,"Chloe to the hospital first."],[3436,3699,"Oh, if she's not okay,"],[3699,3853,"you are done."],[4396,4529,"Oscar."],[4700,4900,"Do you believe me?"],[5201,5292,"The only thing that I know"],[5292,5501,"is that children don't lie."],[6619,6790,"I don't see any reason"],[6790,6973,"for you to stay here anymore."]],"46":[[588,742,"Oscar,"],[742,880,"do you believe me?"],[880,988,"The only thing that I know is"],[988,1105,"that children don't lie."]],"47":[[1126,1222,"I wish days like this"],[1222,1413,"would last a little bit longer."],[1872,1972,"Sleep tight."],[2110,2235,"I promise no one will ever"],[2235,2348,"hurt you again."],[4008,4112,"Damn it! Steven, pull over."]],"48":[[16,166,"Damn it! Steven, pull over."],[333,500,"Oscar, what are you doing?"],[500,717,"Steven, take Chloe to the hospital."],[717,779,"Oscar,"],[779,892,"where are you going?"],[892,971,"You're going back to that"],[971,1159,"bitch, aren't you?"],[1626,1755,"Phoebe, I’m sorry."],[1818,1906,"I shouldn’t have said those"],[1906,2035,"hurtful things."],[3190,3303,"Phoebe?"],[3616,3791,"Where are you?"],[4074,4212,"I'm back."],[4350,4450,"Phoebe?"],[4458,4558,"Phoebe!"],[5776,5897,"Phoebe, where did you go?"]],"49":[[496,588,"Coming back to school"],[588,725,"isn’t so terrible."],[725,825,"Oscar already has"],[825,942,"a wife and child."],[942,1113,"And I have no reason to overstep"],[1113,1326,"in someone else's family."],[1326,1551,"Just what should I do with the babies?"],[1805,2031,"Sorry about that."],[2031,2310,"We're just training over there, and"],[2310,2464,"I didn't see you here."],[2565,2660,"No, thank you."],[2798,2882,"Leo."],[3065,3182,"Phoebe."],[3290,3457,"Are you a student here?"],[3457,3774,"I mean, there's a game later."],[3832,3978,"Are you staying to watch?"],[4016,4133,"No."],[4225,4279,"No, sorry."],[4279,4567,"I'm not interested."],[4567,4704,"Are you sure?"],[4704,4833,"I mean, I'll be playing."],[5601,5772,"Who's that little pup?"],[5860,5997,"Maybe another time."],[6081,6193,"All right."],[6256,6452,"Well, can I at least get your number?"],[6660,6727,"No."],[6869,6952,"You can't."]],"50":[[621,663,"You know what?"],[663,763,"I changed my mind."],[850,942,"Here's my number."],[1130,1201,"You know what?"],[1201,1317,"I would actually"],[1317,1443,"like to go to the game."],[1443,1526,"Phoebe."],[1655,1843,"I can't wait to see you play."],[1843,2035,"I won't let you down."],[2560,2640,"Here."],[2702,2848,"Best seat in the house."],[3286,3357,"Phoebe."],[3411,3507,"It was all my fault, okay?"],[3507,3620,"I should have trusted you"],[3620,3724,"unconditionally."],[3787,3883,"Please,"],[3945,4033,"come home with me."],[4033,4154,"Home? Really?"],[4154,4287,"You mean to your happy little family"],[4287,4529,"with your wife and child?"],[4529,4700,"Sir, that would be a crime."],[4700,4817,"Can we go somewhere"],[4817,4963,"and talk that’s quiet?"],[4963,5109,"It's too risky here."],[5109,5255,"Risky for you maybe."],[5351,5522,"How about you go home"],[5522,5647,"and I'll stay here with Phoebe?"],[6293,6427,"What?"],[6427,6531,"Want to try?"],[6744,6823,"Why not?"],[6886,6948,"Let's just hope you"],[6948,7065,"don't lose too quickly."]],"51":[[834,1005,"Oscar, what are you doing?"],[1005,1071,"This isn't something"],[1071,1263,"you should be doing at your age."],[1263,1455,"What if you get hurt, huh?"],[1455,1643,"Oscar, just go back home, please."],[1826,1943,"You're worried about me?"],[1985,2122,"Scared?"],[2189,2339,"It's not too late to back down."],[2736,2798,"Just sit back"],[2798,2923,"and enjoy the show."],[3265,3482,"Who is that old dude?"],[3482,3657,"Does he really think he could beat Leo?"],[3695,3753,"Leo is the"],[3753,3908,"basketball team captain."],[3937,4070,"He's doomed."],[4070,4149,"But don't you think"],[4149,4325,"he's kind of hot?"],[4325,4458,"I'm honestly rooting for him."],[4458,4512,"What?"],[4512,4696,"Whose team are you on?"],[4925,5055,"So what game you want to play?"],[5205,5326,"1v1."],[5326,5597,"Offense, defense."],[5651,5734,"Now, go."],[6564,6694,"Oh my God!"],[6694,6873,"Did Leo just look at me?"],[6873,6961,"Help!"],[6961,7065,"I can't breathe."],[7282,7403,"Looks like your reflexes"],[7403,7540,"aren’t keeping up, old man."],[7603,7774,"Don't call me that."],[7774,7891,"You're not even qualified to be"],[7891,8012,"a servant in my house."]],"52":[[1810,1843,"All right,"],[1843,1993,"best two out of three."],[2060,2252,"Let's make a bet."],[2252,2373,"What bet?"],[2506,2802,"Loser stays away from Phoebe."],[3040,3174,"I'm going to win this one."],[3278,3449,"Buddy, you've already lost."],[5134,5201,"Help!"],[5201,5501,"Is that old guy winking at me?"],[5597,5772,"What's he doing acting like that?"],[6193,6293,"Hope you can take your loss"],[6293,6360,"like a champ."]],"53":[[166,383,"Sorry, I lost."],[433,596,"I guess I can't ask you out anymore."],[700,817,"It's just a game."],[829,896,"Why is this kid"],[896,1038,"still hanging around?"],[1130,1238,"Phoebe."],[1238,1363,"I think I pulled a muscle"],[1363,1426,"in my arm."],[1530,1651,"It hurts really bad."],[1680,1805,"Where does it hurt?"],[1856,1943,"You know, I told you not to"],[1943,2052,"overexert yourself."],[2097,2173,"He must have ran"],[2173,2323,"into me during the game."],[2394,2565,"It hurts so bad."],[2565,2706,"What? No, I didn't."],[2831,2923,"Ouch."],[2923,2986,"Phoebe. Okay, well."],[3132,3249,"Maybe you can"],[3249,3403,"find me a place to rest."],[3507,3582,"Okay."],[3645,3737,"Oscar?"],[3770,3895,"What are you doing?"],[3999,4079,"Chloe's still waiting"],[4079,4187,"for you at the hospital."]],"54":[[58,221,"Darling, are you all right?"],[221,442,"Are you okay? What happened?"],[688,888,"Leo, maybe let's just grab some food?"],[888,1017,"Give them some privacy."],[1222,1313,"Okay."],[1659,1785,"Mia, you're the only one"],[1785,1851,"who knows the truth"],[1851,2052,"about whose child Chloe really is."],[2052,2139,"Okay, I'm warning you."],[2139,2227,"I will personally"],[2227,2364,"throw you out of the house."],[2364,2452,"Grandpa won't even be"],[2452,2535,"able to save you."],[2827,2911,"Oscar."],[3837,3974,"What's wrong?"],[3974,4095,"Do you not like the food?"],[4095,4195,"No. It's good."],[4283,4379,"That's good."],[4567,4750,"Listen, uh, Phoebe,"],[4854,5159,"I actually really like you."]],"55":[[54,354,"I actually really like you."],[500,554,"From the moment"],[554,654,"that ball was about to hit"],[654,955,"your head, I knew I was done for."],[1067,1263,"I understood what love at"],[1263,1526,"first sight feels like."],[1634,1760,"Hey, here."],[2460,2552,"Yeah, uhm."],[2552,2690,"That's just funny."],[2748,2907,"What if I'm being serious?"],[3132,3315,"Phoebe."],[3315,3457,"Do you want to be my girlfriend?"],[3641,3720,"She doesn't."]],"56":[[262,350,"Oscar, what are you doing here?"],[350,437,"Get out!"],[850,967,"Phoebe, I want to apologize"],[967,1051,"for today."],[1126,1267,"I'm truly sorry."],[1430,1526,"Also, I'm here"],[1526,1659,"because I heard that-"],[1659,1835,"I'm sorry that I have to be"],[1835,1918,"a disturbance"],[1918,2064,"to you and your family."],[2189,2239,"You don't have to"],[2239,2385,"say things you don't mean."],[2965,3123,"Can we go talk alone?"],[3161,3232,"Just for a moment."],[3232,3315,"Can you stop saying"],[3315,3407,"such disgusting things?"],[3407,3536,"I'm trying to eat."],[3536,3595,"Phoebe."],[3595,3699,"Phoebe already said"],[3699,3816,"she doesn't want to talk."]],"57":[[617,709,"You know funny thing is,"],[709,821,"I own this restaurant."],[975,1117,"Let me introduce you to the menu."],[1172,1313,"Is he angry?"],[2110,2256,"We'll have one of each."],[2281,2381,"Right away, sir."],[2448,2615,"It's an important time for you."],[2615,2723,"You need to eat well."],[3795,3958,"You all look hungry."],[3958,4049,"Eat up."],[4049,4212,"This one looks great, Phoebe."],[5309,5380,"It's delicious."],[5380,5497,"You guys should eat, too."]],"58":[[1818,1906,"If everyone's done here,"],[1906,2031,"I think maybe we should go."],[2143,2398,"I got the bill."],[2515,2681,"Well, like I said earlier,"],[2681,2869,"I own this restaurant."],[2869,2994,"It's on me."],[3069,3190,"You probably asked your daddy"],[3190,3345,"for that credit card, didn't you?"],[3457,3591,"You should make him proud."],[3591,3687,"Spend it wisely."]],"59":[[79,204,"Mr. Sinclair, I never thought"],[204,287,"that you would make such"],[287,454,"condescending assumptions."],[600,667,"Come on, let's go."],[842,975,"No, I didn't mean it like that."],[1401,1534,"Shit."],[2481,2660,"Phoebe,"],[2660,2781,"listen."],[2869,2898,"I don't know"],[2898,2982,"what happened between"],[2982,3194,"you and that guy back there,"],[3290,3570,"but when I said I liked you,"],[3570,3670,"I meant it."],[3816,3874,"Hey, just..."],[3874,4016,"Just think it over."],[4295,4637,"Actually, we're married..."],[4637,4913,"and I'm pregnant."],[5192,5301,"You know, this is the first time"],[5301,5388,"anyone's ever"],[5388,5588,"rejected me like that before."],[5651,5801,"You really are different."],[5955,6097,"She's not joking."],[6189,6314,"The baby's mine."],[6690,7036,"So you really are his wife?"],[7144,7211,"Yes."]],"60":[[16,133,"So I was out from the start,"],[133,208,"wasn't I?"],[266,333,"No, don't say that."],[333,462,"I mean, we could still be friends,"],[462,542,"right?"],[658,746,"No, I think, uh,"],[796,921,"I think I just need some time"],[1001,1059,"alone."],[1126,1247,"Leo. Wait, Leo!"],[1630,1672,"Let me go."],[1672,1797,"I don't want to be with a jerk like you."],[1797,1922,"Yes, I'm a jerk."],[1922,1985,"All right?"],[2106,2227,"I don't know when this all started,"],[2227,2423,"but when I see you with another man,"],[2423,2627,"I get consumed with jealousy."],[2823,3019,"I want to go before it gets too late."],[4312,4450,"When I see you with another man,"],[4450,4617,"I get consumed with jealousy."]],"61":[[429,533,"Oscar."],[738,880,"Do you believe me?"],[1138,1234,"The only thing that I know"],[1234,1430,"is that children don't lie."],[1539,1705,"Which one is the real him?"],[3165,3274,"Are you crazy?"],[3274,3457,"I'd do anything to get my wife back."],[3678,3807,"Phoebe, I was wrong."],[3878,4008,"Okay, I should have trusted you."],[4108,4258,"I lost my head when I saw you"],[4258,4433,"sign that check by the pool."],[4462,4558,"But I know there must have"],[4558,4633,"been more to it."],[4750,4904,"So from here on out,"],[4904,5030,"no matter what."],[5209,5405,"I'll always stand by your side."],[5492,5593,"Actually, by the pool,"],[5593,5705,"I didn't..."],[6160,6306,"You don't have to explain."],[6385,6473,"I already know."]],"62":[[759,888,"I'm nervous."],[1021,1159,"Don't be nervous."],[1368,1514,"I'll help you relax."],[2915,3028,"Relax."],[3607,3695,"Phoebe."],[4016,4120,"I love you."],[4688,4829,"I'm a little scared."],[4879,4979,"Baby, please."],[5080,5180,"Don't worry."],[5238,5338,"I'll be careful."],[6068,6151,"Oscar."],[6552,6648,"I love you too."]],"63":[[633,734,"So, uhm..."],[759,913,"Phoebe’s baby bump"],[934,1051,"is getting bigger."],[1092,1217,"Why is, uh..."],[1238,1347,"Chloe's paternity test"],[1347,1468,"taking so long?"],[1910,2068,"Well, the results were ready,"],[2102,2168,"but I was worried"],[2168,2235,"that someone might have"],[2235,2302,"tampered with it."],[2302,2481,"So I got a trusted doctor"],[2481,2640,"to run the test again."],[2656,2740,"Good."],[2740,2848,"Well done."],[2911,3011,"You know, grandpa"],[3178,3294,"Phoebe's graduating soon."],[3382,3566,"And with everything that's happened,"],[3649,3778,"I plan on marrying her"],[3778,3933,"as soon as possible."],[3953,4070,"Oscar."],[4212,4375,"You have to understand."],[4458,4550,"I want you to"],[4550,4733,"marry the person that you love."],[4934,5059,"I love Phoebe."],[5084,5226,"Excellent."],[5226,5401,"I will throw you two an"],[5401,5605,"once-in-a-lifetime wedding."],[5826,5922,"You know,"],[6056,6252,"the company's succession"],[6327,6560,"has always been reserved for you."],[6673,6752,"So,"],[6898,6981,"next week,"],[6981,7157,"I'm going to host the banquet"],[7157,7328,"and announce"],[7328,7378,"that you are"],[7378,7532,"the new head of the board"],[7532,7640,"of the Sinclair Group."],[7724,8020,"And we'll reveal Phoebe's identity."]],"64":[[825,1080,"This is your promotion party."],[1080,1284,"Why am I dressed like this?"],[1372,1476,"That's a secret."],[1647,1730,"Boss,"],[1730,1847,"Mason Trump wants to discuss"],[1847,1947,"with you the collaboration for the"],[1947,2089,"home retirement project."],[2160,2256,"He's waiting outside."],[2285,2448,"Tell him to come to the banquet hall."],[2585,2660,"Phoebe's pregnant."],[2660,2756,"I need to stay with her."],[2794,2952,"I'll be fine."],[2952,3053,"You go ahead."],[3244,3420,"Go get yourself something to eat."],[3536,3645,"I'll be right back."],[4838,5067,"As long as that baby's alive,"],[5067,5209,"it's a threat to us."],[5455,5672,"Well, now that Oscar's gone,"],[5672,5826,"it's a perfect time to..."],[5905,6014,"get rid of it."]],"65":[[95,279,"Hey girl,"],[279,492,"it must feel so great to finally"],[492,667,"feel like the swan"],[667,754,"when you're used to living"],[754,867,"like the ugly duckling."],[950,1021,"Wait,"],[1134,1330,"where are you off to so quickly?"],[1330,1393,"Don't you want to know"],[1393,1584,"the baby's DNA results?"],[1584,1680,"I think you and I both know"],[1680,1872,"that Chloe isn’t Oscar's daughter."],[1922,2064,"I have nothing to worry about."],[2064,2193,"You bitch."],[2193,2260,"You know you can't just"],[2260,2448,"marry into the Sinclair family."],[2523,2736,"Robert's only keeping you around"],[2736,2944,"because that baby in your belly."],[2990,3186,"When the time comes,"],[3186,3390,"he might just keep it,"],[3390,3490,"and kick you out."],[3712,3849,"First off, I married Oscar,"],[3849,4024,"not the Sinclair family."],[4024,4079,"And second,"],[4079,4179,"grandpa is not like that."],[4179,4325,"He's not that kind of person."],[4362,4475,"You know,"],[4475,4700,"she's just a bitch who stole from me."],[4758,5025,"Let's see if she's still that cocky"],[5025,5150,"when she loses the baby."]],"66":[[16,283,"Let's see if she's still that cocky"],[283,425,"when she loses the baby."],[759,829,"Watch out."],[3182,3361,"You and your bastard"],[3361,3595,"baby can go to hell together."],[3670,3795,"Hey! Get away from my wife!"],[3795,3870,"Oscar."]],"67":[[679,750,"I'm going to kill you"],[750,888,"someday, I swear to God!"],[980,1201,"Oscar, you got it all wrong."],[1201,1284,"Phoebe over here,"],[1284,1430,"she just slipped."],[1830,1893,"Oscar!"],[1893,2043,"How dare you hit me?"],[2043,2185,"I feel like killing you, too."],[2185,2277,"This isn't over."],[2277,2394,"You two better sleep with one eye"],[2394,2494,"open at night!"],[3269,3345,"Wait. We can't leave."],[3345,3478,"This is your promotion party."],[3478,3553,"We got to take care"],[3553,3678,"of your injuries first."],[3678,3870,"Nothing is more important than you."],[3958,4066,"Cancel the banquet."]],"68":[[592,734,"Be gentle, please."],[767,950,"I'm already being very careful."],[970,1030,"Ow."],[1063,1188,"Okay, you know what?"],[1188,1276,"Get out of there."],[1276,1363,"I'll do it myself."],[3232,3349,"How's Phoebe doing?"],[3603,3766,"I haven't even come after you yet."],[3858,4049,"How dare you show your faces here."],[4049,4095,"Oscar."],[4095,4266,"This is all a misunderstanding."],[4362,4437,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[4437,4554,"the results of the DNA test"],[4554,4671,"you requested earlier."],[4671,4733,"They're ready."]],"69":[[408,500,"That's impossible."],[500,642,"You tampered with it, didn't you?"],[896,1017,"There's no way Chloe"],[1017,1109,"can be my daughter."],[1109,1209,"Oscar,"],[1209,1334,"there's no way I could"],[1334,1463,"have tampered with the results."],[1526,1676,"Chloe is your daughter."],[1972,2156,"Chloe is Oscar's daughter."],[2218,2310,"Oscar."],[2310,2456,"You chose the hospital."],[2456,2652,"The doctor is one of your people."],[2652,2773,"Do you really think Mia could"],[2773,2932,"manipulate everything?"],[2932,3119,"I mean, right under your nose."],[3290,3370,"Mia, no."],[3370,3528,"She couldn't."],[3528,3582,"But that doesn't"],[3582,3732,"mean someone else couldn't."],[3933,4233,"I mean, why would I help Mia?"],[4233,4325,"You having another"],[4325,4433,"heir only makes things"],[4433,4554,"worse for me."],[4554,4708,"Oscar,"],[4708,4817,"be a man."],[4817,4996,"Take responsibility."],[4996,5259,"I mean, even though you love Phoebe,"],[5259,5422,"you still have to take care of"],[5422,5601,"Mia and Chloe."],[5793,5930,"So the report says that Chloe's"],[5930,6093,"your biological daughter?"],[6093,6189,"Yes,"],[6247,6327,"but..."]],"70":[[29,145,"Yes."],[200,237,"But..."],[237,283,"Enough,"],[283,362,"no buts."],[571,684,"Thank you for taking care of me"],[684,842,"these past few days."],[913,1038,"But I'm leaving immediately."],[1084,1226,"That report is wrong."],[1226,1363,"Okay, give me a chance."],[1363,1438,"Give me some time,"],[1438,1555,"and I can figure this out."],[1555,1634,"Hold on, hold on."],[1634,1897,"Look, you don't have to move out."],[1897,2056,"I mean, after all the children"],[2056,2252,"you are carrying are Sinclair's."],[2252,2356,"You’re family."],[2356,2606,"I don't care about the Sinclairs."],[2606,2798,"I care about my child."],[2798,2911,"And what is best for them"],[2911,3036,"is for them to be happy."],[3123,3261,"Do you really want your child"],[3261,3382,"to grow up with two moms"],[3382,3449,"and one dad?"],[3807,3953,"I didn't think so."],[3960,4166,"Please, you have to believe me."],[4166,4225,"Let me go."],[4283,4441,"Or I can't promise what I’ll do."],[6352,6452,"You'll regret this."]],"71":[[1234,1397,"What are you doing?"],[2068,2139,"Dr. Davies."],[2160,2281,"There's no need to be afraid."],[2281,2339,"We just want"],[2339,2477,"the real DNA test results."],[2740,2806,"Who are you?"],[3103,3165,"You need to understand"],[3165,3294,"who the real boss is here."],[3411,3524,"We don't want much,"],[3524,3628,"just the truth."],[4350,4471,"Mom."],[4821,4971,"I won’t forgive him again."],[5038,5109,"Oh, Phoebe."],[5267,5401,"Look, mom’ll stand by"],[5401,5584,"whatever decision you make."],[7390,7474,"Why are you here?"],[7474,7595,"You are not welcome."],[7595,7682,"Phoebe, I want to ask you"],[7682,7828,"to come home with me."],[7828,7882,"I have something"],[7882,8020,"very important to tell you."]],"72":[[625,754,"Oh."],[829,925,"So,"],[1017,1138,"all that crying about"],[1138,1372,"yesterday was just an act, huh?"],[1543,1655,"Mia, I'm giving you ten minutes"],[1655,1747,"to pack your things"],[1747,1897,"and get out of my house."],[1897,2022,"And if you're still not gone,"],[2022,2227,"my staff is going to kick you out."],[2427,2535,"Oscar."],[2585,2794,"What are you doing?"],[2794,2877,"Do you want me"],[2877,3094,"and my sweet little baby Chloe"],[3094,3303,"to be thrown out on the street?"],[3499,3582,"Daddy,"],[3582,3816,"do you not want me or mommy anymore?"],[3870,4091,"Oscar, you're heartless!"],[4091,4141,"How could you"],[4141,4371,"just throw out your own daughter?"],[4429,4512,"Grandpa,"],[4675,4975,"this is the real DNA test report."],[5013,5188,"The previous one"],[5188,5330,"is the one William tampered with."],[5330,5488,"And he bribed the doctor."],[5488,5605,"That's bullshit!"],[5776,5822,"I mean,"],[5847,6010,"why would I bribe the doctor?"],[6010,6106,"I have no reason to."],[6106,6181,"I mean,"],[6264,6368,"you having another heir"],[6368,6519,"just makes things worse for me."],[6727,6781,"Grandpa,"],[6810,6944,"do not believe his nonsense."],[6944,7082,"I don't know why you would do it."],[7278,7382,"I have proof."],[7511,7553,"Grandpa,"],[7553,7645,"this is surveillance"],[7645,7828,"footage of William bribing the doctor,"],[7857,7966,"and there's transactional"],[7966,8037,"records in here."],[8083,8224,"If we get rid of Oscar,"],[8224,8316,"I'll be the sole heir of"],[8316,8400,"the Sinclair family."]],"73":[[37,237,"This is illegal, you know."],[237,387,"What are you afraid of?"],[387,529,"If we get rid of Oscar."],[529,725,"I’ll be the sole heir of Sinclair family."],[759,896,"And you can be"],[896,1038,"the director of the hospital."],[1447,1526,"Come on, grandpa."],[1526,1647,"Obviously, that video is fake."],[1647,1739,"I mean,"],[1793,1901,"don't believe Oscar."],[1901,2168,"Okay, video can be edited."],[2168,2256,"But what about those bank"],[2256,2327,"statements?"],[2327,2427,"All those transfers"],[2427,2548,"are those fake too?"],[2660,2798,"This is obviously a setup."],[2798,2927,"I don't even know that doctor."],[3094,3361,"One thing I feared"],[3361,3661,"was you two ripping each other apart."],[3874,3974,"Unfortunately,"],[3974,4091,"it's happened."],[5267,5422,"I declare"],[5534,5684,"Oscar Sinclair,"],[5684,5839,"the new head of the board"],[5839,5951,"of the Sinclair Group."],[6156,6297,"Effective immediately."]],"74":[[362,508,"Grandpa, I can explain."],[508,700,"This is all Oscar’s scheme."],[700,888,"I didn't do anything wrong."],[1376,1451,"Mia,"],[1526,1618,"pack your things"],[1618,1718,"and get out of my house"],[1718,1785,"immediately."],[1914,2002,"Do you want me"],[2002,2310,"and my sweet little girl to be"],[2310,2494,"homeless rats?"],[2932,3003,"Cry."],[3695,3891,"Consider this your final warning."],[3891,3966,"If I catch you"],[3966,4133,"trying to hurt Phoebe again,"],[4200,4329,"I'll kill you myself."],[4446,4596,"Mommy, I’m scared."],[4596,4767,"Oh, It’s okay, baby."],[5146,5296,"Oscar, wait."],[5459,5601,"Just wait."],[5601,5701,"I'll catch you slipping"],[5701,5818,"sooner or later."]],"75":[[400,483,"You know, everything is"],[483,613,"happier than I imagined"],[613,742,"it would be."],[742,984,"Everyday I can feel the baby kicking."],[984,1121,"And I just"],[1267,1426,"I love them even more."],[1626,1735,"It's like"],[2010,2118,"like nothing in this world"],[2118,2243,"could bother me anymore."],[2268,2369,"Oh, really?"],[2544,2631,"Well, I guess I should"],[2631,2769,"wear you out more next time."],[3140,3328,"What you should be worried about"],[3328,3432,"is our wedding."],[3432,3524,"What?"],[3628,3774,"Our wedding?"],[3774,3845,"Why?"],[3933,4074,"Are you backing out now?"],[4154,4341,"You said yes to my proposal"],[4341,4446,"in front of your mom."],[4521,4662,"I just wasn't expecting"],[4662,4800,"it'd happen so soon."],[4854,5042,"For me, it can't come soon enough."]],"76":[[20,241,"I wish I could marry you today."],[821,938,"Phoebe."],[1117,1213,"The ceremony wasn't"],[1213,1401,"complete before."],[2002,2160,"Will you marry me?"],[2344,2498,"For real this time?"],[2919,3219,"Yes, yes."],[3561,3649,"A thousand times yes."]],"77":[[246,387,"You must be tired from the past"],[387,487,"few days."],[554,646,"No, not at all."],[646,825,"I'm just excited for our wedding."],[888,975,"Dear."],[975,1071,"I'm Vivian,"],[1071,1217,"your wedding dress designer."],[1255,1372,"Hi."],[1422,1543,"Oh, I'm Phoebe."],[1634,1705,"It has your name"],[1705,1826,"written all over it."],[1826,2002,"I'm sure you're going to love it."],[2435,2519,"Ready?"],[4029,4154,"Go try it on, my bride."],[4287,4450,"Take this to the fitting room."],[4450,4537,"Come with me."],[5643,5751,"Let's welcome Phoebe."],[6356,6443,"Phoebe,"],[6443,6548,"will you marry me?"],[6598,6631,"Yes."],[6919,7019,"Mr. Sinclair,"],[7094,7178,"she's ready."]],"78":[[2235,2289,"Are you happy"],[2289,2439,"with what you're seeing?"],[2485,2602,"Just perfect."],[2777,2882,"I can't even articulate"],[2882,3061,"how I feel right now."],[3274,3395,"You’re perfect."],[3482,3616,"Do you know that?"],[3616,3732,"I know."],[3845,3995,"I imagined you in a wedding dress"],[3995,4183,"so many times in my head."],[4350,4504,"Does it match what you imagined?"],[4575,4708,"It's even better."],[4854,4992,"So much so that"],[5067,5284,"this groom is having trouble resisting"],[5284,5413,"kissing his bride right now."]],"79":[[2652,2744,"Phoebe."],[2844,2998,"Say you love me."],[4041,4116,"Let's go home."]],"80":[[1480,1639,"Why are the lights off?"],[2610,2719,"Don't worry."],[2819,2890,"I'm here."],[2998,3119,"Let’s have a seat."],[3119,3240,"No need to sit."],[3340,3470,"Her things are packed."],[3516,3670,"Take her and get out."],[3849,4029,"Grandpa, what is going on?"],[4029,4308,"I trusted both of you completely."],[4346,4617,"And this is how you repay me?"],[4662,4767,"What happened? What is that?"],[4767,4842,"I have no idea"],[4842,4929,"what you're talking about."],[4929,4979,"Oh, you don't know what"],[4979,5067,"I'm talking about?"],[5105,5271,"How do you explain this"],[5271,5563,"surrogacy contract that you signed?"],[5563,5722,"I know everything now."],[5722,5843,"Phoebe's a surrogate."]],"81":[[54,225,"Wife, child, family."],[291,312,"And if you're"],[312,471,"thinking of adopting, or worse,"],[471,604,"a surrogate, you can kiss"],[604,746,"the company goodbye."],[863,1017,"Grandpa, I'm sorry."],[1146,1192,"I'm sorry."],[1192,1330,"This is all my fault."],[1330,1443,"Phoebe, don't do this."],[1443,1655,"You did nothing wrong."],[1655,1780,"This doesn't mean anything."],[1780,1810,"Okay,"],[1810,1926,"what I'm telling you right now"],[1926,2081,"is that I love Phoebe."],[2185,2310,"Yeah."],[2310,2489,"Quite the act, isn't it?"],[2556,2773,"Deceiving an old man"],[2773,2815,"pulled out"],[2815,3032,"all the stops, to even drawing up"],[3032,3232,"a marriage contract."],[3232,3286,"Well, since it's"],[3286,3445,"just a contract, it's invalid."],[3445,3503,"Grandpa-"],[3503,3603,"What a shame."],[3661,3820,"I actually liked you."],[3945,4108,"But as it turns out,"],[4175,4229,"you were just"],[4229,4408,"with Oscar for the money."],[4608,4825,"Get a divorce and get out!"],[4825,4934,"Grandpa, I'm telling you"],[4934,5113,"right now that I love Phoebe."],[5113,5280,"It was fake in the beginning,"],[5280,5363,"but this is real."],[5363,5572,"I can't trust a liar"],[5572,5768,"who would be with my grandson"],[5768,5897,"just for the money."]],"82":[[29,179,"I’m so sorry."],[304,450,"Look, I'm sorry for everything that"],[450,546,"I've done."],[692,825,"But please,"],[900,992,"please,"],[1055,1234,"don't take this out on Oscar."],[1451,1576,"Look,at the time, my..."],[1718,1839,"my mom was in the hospital"],[1839,2014,"and she's severely ill."],[2210,2427,"I just really needed the money."],[2740,2790,"And Oscar."],[2790,2936,"Oscar is just..."],[3111,3299,"he was just trying to help me."],[3724,3883,"I'll move out"],[3966,4091,"immediately."],[4091,4183,"Phoebe."]],"83":[[925,1113,"Grandpa trusted me."],[1326,1539,"He trusted me so much."],[1668,1780,"Listen to me."],[1860,2052,"This is not your fault."],[2135,2223,"God, I knew"],[2223,2360,"I knew I should've told him."],[2448,2748,"It's just one lie led to another."],[2911,3107,"God, I’m terrible."],[3215,3370,"Oscar, what do I do?"],[3503,3557,"What do I do?"],[3557,3720,"I mean, I..."],[3720,3824,"I don't have any other reason"],[3824,3953,"to stay here anymore."],[3953,4083,"I mean, grandpa doesn't trust me."],[4237,4366,"I mean, what do I do?"],[4542,4688,"I truly love you,"],[4688,4871,"and he's not gonna believe me."]],"84":[[33,179,"I truly love you,"],[179,408,"and he’s not gonna believe me."],[408,604,"I'll handle it. Okay?"],[675,855,"Just let me fix it."],[930,1017,"You just go upstairs,"],[1017,1134,"you get some rest."],[1188,1222,"Phoebe,"],[1222,1326,"when you wake up tomorrow,"],[1326,1430,"it'll all be better."],[1622,1760,"No."],[1964,2093,"No, I can't stay here"],[2093,2198,"until he believes me."],[2310,2439,"Stay at my place then."],[2494,2556,"Okay?"],[2585,2740,"I'll settle things here,"],[2781,2890,"then you can come back."],[3011,3082,"I am..."],[3157,3282,"I'm just gonna stay with mom"],[3282,3395,"at the hospital."],[3528,3582,"I think she's going to be"],[3582,3799,"discharged soon anyway, so..."],[3895,3991,"Okay."],[3991,4116,"One night"],[4229,4295,"and I'll come get you"],[4295,4437,"and bring you back."],[4479,4683,"Just promise me"],[4917,5138,"you'll come for me soon, okay?"],[5196,5280,"Promise."]],"85":[[458,633,"What are you doing here?"],[633,750,"Is she gone?"],[750,905,"She's gone."],[905,1042,"As you wished."],[1272,1447,"It's probably for the best."],[1447,1488,"Grandpa,"],[1488,1539,"are you really"],[1539,1659,"going to cut off Phoebe"],[1659,1835,"just because of some papers?"],[1864,2056,"Did you not learn anything about her?"],[2056,2185,"All I know is"],[2185,2364,"she was willing to have your child"],[2364,2569,"and be with you only for money."],[2569,2731,"You really have lost it."],[2731,2965,"I told you, it's not about Phoebe."],[2965,3098,"I'm going to marry her."],[3098,3232,"I lost it."],[3232,3370,"Well, you know, I probably have"],[3370,3520,"letting you two fool me."],[3520,3616,"And I don't care"],[3616,3774,"that you were the mastermind."],[3774,3953,"She had her part in it, too."],[3953,4133,"And I will not allow some woman"],[4133,4333,"who would sell her soul for money"],[4333,4483,"to be my granddaughter-in-law."],[4483,4571,"Oh, is that so?"],[4696,4800,"Well, then the Sinclair Group"],[4800,4900,"is not worth inheriting."]],"86":[[4,104,"Well, then the Sinclair Group"],[104,221,"is not worth inheriting."],[287,404,"What do you mean?"],[404,675,"You would give up your place as heir"],[675,763,"for a woman?"],[763,867,"Grandpa, you are being"],[867,1084,"so contradictory."],[1084,1222,"You used the inheritance"],[1222,1284,"to force me"],[1284,1418,"into a marriage in the beginning."],[1418,1463,"And now that"],[1463,1543,"I found the love of"],[1543,1626,"my life, you're going"],[1626,1793,"to threaten me with it?"],[1851,1926,"Not this time."],[1926,2127,"I will not let you manipulate me."],[3361,3591,"You really love Phoebe that much?"],[3657,3766,"Boss."],[3828,3949,"There’s something wrong."],[3949,4020,"Phoebe."],[4120,4200,"Phoebe is missing."]],"87":[[771,871,"Oh."],[913,1051,"Good morning darling."],[1388,1526,"What’s going on?"],[2469,2648,"Mia, kidnapping is a crime."],[2736,2961,"I've got nothing left."],[2986,3244,"You've taken everything from me."],[3411,3616,"Because of you."],[3649,3866,"Why should you"],[3945,4058,"get to marry Oscar,"],[4058,4233,"and I don't, hmm?"],[4408,4696,"Doesn't seem too fair, does it?"],[4783,5005,"Please, just..."],[5196,5359,"Chloe, think about Chloe..."],[5601,5739,"Chloe?"],[5739,5847,"Chloe, come on."],[5880,6018,"Oscar won't even take Chloe in."],[6018,6097,"You know that"],[6097,6297,"because it's from you!"]],"88":[[0,175,"It's your fault."],[175,337,"You know why?"],[667,767,"Because you're pregnant"],[767,900,"with his baby."],[900,1076,"Oh, yeah."],[1155,1397,"But how does he know that"],[1397,1647,"you're not lying about that?"],[1680,1740,"Hm?"],[3107,3182,"Where?"],[3253,3315,"Found it,"],[3315,3432,"they're in the last operating room."],[3432,3536,"Police are already on their way."],[3661,3795,"He's only marrying you"],[3795,4095,"because of this little bastard"],[4095,4237,"in your belly."],[4329,4454,"Let's cut it out now."],[4571,4729,"He's not gonna want you anymore."],[4821,4967,"Let's take a gamble."],[5046,5347,"One...two."],[5526,5605,"Help me!"]],"89":[[588,779,"Phoebe, I am so sorry I'm late."],[934,1092,"Get off me."],[1163,1238,"Are you okay?"],[1964,2131,"Steven, take her to the police."],[2131,2277,"I want her locked up for life."],[2277,2389,"No Oscar! Got it."],[2494,2690,"Get off of me! Oscar!"],[2690,2769,"You're not gonna get away with this."],[2769,2873,"You rat bitch!"],[2873,2982,"You’re not even pregnant."],[3098,3178,"Oscar."],[3386,3541,"The babies are coming."],[3566,3661,"What?"],[3716,3832,"Deep breath. Come on."],[3832,3958,"Everybody, clear the hall."],[3970,4091,"Move, move, move."],[4909,5034,"We got to get this patient stabilized."],[5034,5159,"I'm gonna need you to stay out here."]],"90":[[1659,1864,"This is all my fault."],[1956,2127,"It’s all my fault."],[2423,2631,"Why did I have to make it so"],[2631,2773,"difficult on Phoebe?"],[3023,3165,"What if something happens to her?"],[3269,3436,"What am I going to do?"],[3666,3837,"Breathe."],[3837,3966,"Push."],[4066,4120,"Push!"],[4170,4258,"Breathe."],[4725,4884,"Why is it taking so long?"],[4946,5075,"Breathe."],[5100,5150,"Push."],[5150,5280,"Hold your breath."],[5280,5388,"And push."],[5388,5655,"That's it. Almost there."],[5655,5730,"Just like that."],[5839,5972,"Yes. Yes."]],"91":[[513,583,"Phoebe."],[663,788,"Congratulations."],[788,946,"Two 